title: Five Minutes of Missing Audio
description:
After Minifans raise questions about missing audio from the first ever episode of the Kirk Minihane Show, Minihane wonders how he should deal with a producer who deleted audio without telling him.


You can find every episode of this show on Apple Podcasts, Spotify or YouTube. Prime Members can listen ad-free on Amazon Music. For more, visit barstool.link/kminshow
